channel.title: Mage bank problem
channel.description:
Basically when hovering over where the lever is it doesn't even give you the option to "teleport" my mouse is hovered over it where it should allow you to click it and be teleported out of the wilderness. Wasn't sure if this was client, or server sided. Has anyone else ran into this problem before? It's as if the lever isn't even there as an object.
[img]http://i.imgur.com/1KF6sfR.png[/img]

item.title: Mage bank problem
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

It’s client sided.

Either A:
You need to add this: http://www.rune-server.org/runescape-development/rs2-client/help/487583-object-interaction-support-32k.html

Or B:
You don’t have the object definitions and you need to hardcode them.
